item.title: CVE-2022-4551|2024-08-03T01:41:45.582Z -- unknown -- rich%20table%20of%20contents
item.description: The Rich Table of Contents WordPress plugin before 1.3.9 does not validate and escape some of its shortcode attributes before outputting them back in a page/post where the shortcode is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks
